Duuuudee. As a junior member youre destined to lose this argument against a senior member. Come back when youre mature enough to understand we dont really care what you think.

@ people who think gravedigs are okay.
Stop trying to tell everyone you think gravedigs are okay, because theyre not. If you werent a part of the community when the topic was hot, its your own damn fault, the topics probably dead for a reason. If you want to get consent from a moderator about gravedigging go ahead, because its probably a good topic then, but for shitty skillcapes that people could make in 5 minutes that probably arent even animated its not worth it, learn to model and make em yourself. I have no doubt that people will continue to gravedig, but if this got through to at least one person, then im proud of my accomplishments.
